#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:77
msgid ""
"A new campaign, Winds of Fate, has been added to the game! This is the first "
"Drake campaign to be included in Wesnoth, showing their fight for survival "
"and return to Wesnoth’s Great Continent as they flee their shrinking and "
"sinking island home."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:79
msgid ""
"Eastern Invasion - the first Loyalist campaign ever added to Wesnoth - has "
"been completely remade to add more variety to its scenarios, give more "
"personality to its characters, make the AI more interesting to play against, "
"and to fix several lore conflicts with other campaigns."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><div><p>
#: template.html:81
msgid ""
"And lastly, the Quenoth faction in the campaign Under the Burning Suns has "
"been given an overhaul to make them more interesting - hero units can now "
"gain unique bonuses when leveling up while regular units have new abilities "
"and new weapon effects for their attacks, making this a unique experience "
"among Wesnoth’s campaigns."
msgstr ""

